data.description: This one owner, Carriage Hills home features an open concept, split bedroom floor plan. It has wonderful natural light throughout. The primary suite has a door that opens to the back porch. The primary bathroom has a fully tiled shower and separate soaking tub. Three additional bedrooms and a bathroom are on the other side of the home. The kitchen has a spacious, counter height island and stained cabinets while the living room features built-in shelves and shiplap detailing adorns the electric fireplace. The front and backyard have been landscaped and are a garden lover's dream! Sellers are offering $7500 your way!
